y, decision\u2011making under pressure, and the impact on crew dynamics, **Candidate\u202fD** offers the most robust combination of strengths for a long\u2011distance pilot role, with interpersonal drawbacks that appear more manageable than the communication and health issues of the other candidates.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate D\"}"}
